{"tid":719314,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"何wayne充分解釋兩球12m判決 一巴巴車落班迷朗到","createTime":"2018-06-27T10:31:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-27T12:49:34.000Z","uid":173160,"like":97,"dislike":71,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"2bd65c1c662263cae46eaf65b55bca4d8dc55eb5","tid":719314,"uid":173160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T10:31:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5dF8FzjoRcM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D5dF8FzjoRcM&d=sdiwd3qVr6FK2OrUAZn90P755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=bab56f92\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5dF8FzjoRcM</a><br />\n<br />\n第一粒黑哨12m<br />\n9:40 <br />\n 馬斯手部動作輕微<br />\n尼日利亞球員本來就無進攻機會   完全無理據 判12m<br />\n<br />\n10:50<br />\n第二粒  無吹12m係正確判決<br />\n盧祖 波打中手  令到尼日利亞有黃金機會 但射失<br />\n由於得益 所以係唔需要判12m<br />\n<br />\n一條片輕鬆一巴一巴車落D盲反到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而家阿根庭比人黑左一球都未出聲,班狗仲要惡人先告狀<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc22246db3ae1e34180740031e3396549d66845d","tid":719314,"uid":173160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T10:40:33.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"648032b34b091b89c09917cafe392287571f4a7d","tid":719314,"uid":70201,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T10:42:51.000Z","msg":"盲反狗不敢面對 只敢默默留下負皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/nor